title: Game of Thrones finale dissection
body:
Game of Thrones finale dissection

We’re finally through. No more wondering who would sit on the iron throne anymore. No more who will survive anymore. The reality of season finale of game of thrones exceeded our worst ideas.

Season 8 got extremely low ratings in comparison to its previous glory. Well except for first 2 episodes of season 8. Remember all of those reunions and sailing ships? It all went downhill with episode 3 –…

description:
Chapter 2 is up and running!

Chapters: 2/?
Fandom: A Song of Ice and Fire - George R. R. Martin, Game of Thrones (TV)
Rating: Mature
Warnings: No Archive Warnings Apply
Relationships: Arya Stark/Gendry Waters
Characters: Arya Stark, Gendry Waters, Davos Seaworth, Tyrion Lannister, Brienne of Tarth, Yara Greyjoy, Samwell Tarly, Bran Stark, Bronn (ASoIaF), Sansa Stark
Summary:

Despite his humble origins, Gendry Baratheon is named king of Westeros, with Ser Arya Stark serving as his Master of War. Gendry is burning the candle at both ends: rebuilding the city during the day and secretly loving a woman at night.

“You have nothing to say about that?” He asked, raising her chin with his hand and forcing her to look at him.

“I’m the Master of War, not your Hand.”

“I am not asking my Master of War right now, I am asking the woman who is presently naked in my furs.”
